= redis安装

仅在centos8下安装

== 安装

[console,bash]
----
dnf install redis
----

== 配置

设置开机启动
[console,bash]
----
systemctl enable redis
----

启动
[console,bash]
----
systemctl start redis
----

重启
[console,bash]
----
systemctl restart redis
----

关闭
[console,bash]
----
systemctl stop redis
----

从空密码设置密码
[console,bash]
----
redis-cli
config set requirepass foo_password
----